<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>1986-12-31</DATELINE><TITLE>Immune-mediated diseases of the dog and cat III. Immune-mediated diseases of the integumentary, urogenital, endocrine and vascular systems</TITLE><BODY>Abstract The first two articles in this series have covered the basis of the immune mediated diseases, systemic immune-mediated diseases and those that involve the haemolymphatic and musculoskeletal system. The purpose of this article is to cover the immune-mediated diseases that involve the integumentary, urogenital, endocrine and vascular systems.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>